{"tid":264951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[你問禾答]  畀人控告非禮     最後成功甩身 !!!!!!!    吹咩","createTime":"2017-05-31T09:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T09:13:05.000Z","uid":82646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc539455e820317a441344a91cdab5ad76ff62ed","tid":264951,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"南亞裔向護士申淫爪  離奇理由脫罪    <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170531/photo/bkn-20170531162259648-0531_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170531163158\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170531%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170531162259648-0531_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170531163158&h=913948f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已婚<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">南亞裔</span></span>男醫生來港參與交流計劃，期間他在伊利沙伯醫院護士宿舍的男更衣室內，被指趁實習男<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">護士下身仍未穿好褲子時</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">涉嫌拍打男護士臀部和摸對方的大腿內側</span></span>，事後被控一項非禮罪。被告今日在九龍城法院被裁定<span style=\"color: red;\">罪名不成立。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">裁判官指</span></span>，45歲被告Ghosh Sandip<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有復發性甩骹，不能否定案發時他只想請男事主幫忙</span></span>。此外，男事主雖指<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被告當時面帶笑容</span></span>，但裁判官認為，這<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不代表被告當時不感痛楚</span></span>，尤其是他<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想事主幫忙，為表禮貌才面露微笑</span></span>，故裁定他罪名不成立。<br />\n0"},{"pid":"b5a9b17269be867470242e59dff3689be4dc65be","tid":264951,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/171303_c41406143c8d921cfef606129e9f32b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F171303_c41406143c8d921cfef606129e9f32b7.jpg&h=81956911&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}